    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><blockquote>
<p>此贴用于记录<strong>broland</strong>中的地点所对应的坐标。</p>
</blockquote>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="地下家园-259-60"><a href="#地下家园-259-60" class="headerlink" title="地下家园 (-259 ~ 60)"></a>地下家园 (-259 ~ 60)</h2><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/01/26/tZMES6UDojxrzs9.png" alt="home.png"><br><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/01/26/24MUCRFmiXgB8bP.png" alt="home.png"><br><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/01/26/C5caOtAMmnBhN84.png" alt="home.png">  </p>
